  • Classes in org.joo.steak.framework.event used by org.joo.steak.framework 
    Class and Description
    StateChangedDispatcher
    This is mainly used by State to dispatch StateChangedEvent to StateManager when it finishes its task and want to move on.
    StateChangedEvent
    This event indicates a state (wish to) changed
    StateChangedListener
    A listener will receive StateChangedEvent When used for StateManager it will find the next state and move to that state.
    StateEngineDispatcher
    This is mainly used by StateManager to dispatch an event when it starts/finishes
